FBIS4-60146 "drnes099_n_94011" FBIS-NES-94-099 Daily Report 22 May 1994 LEBANON Reaction to al-Dirani Seizure Reported Reaction to al-Dirani Seizure Reported Fundamentalists Threaten Reprisal NC2205155494 Kafr Killa Voice of the South in Arabic 1530 GMT 22 May 94 NC2205155494 Kafr Killa Voice of the South Arabic BFN [Text] REUTER cites fundamentalist officials in Beirut as saying that members of their group are preparing to launch a spectacular operation against the Israelis to avenge the kidnapping of Mustafa al-Dirani, military official in charge of the so-called Believers Group, in al-Biqa' at dawn yesterday.
